flash.tools.debugger

Interface ILaunchNotification


  • public interface ILaunchNotification
    Used to notify caller in case of ADL Exit Code 1: Successful invocation of an already running AIR application. ADL exits immediately.
    Author:
    sakkus

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void notify(IOException e)
      Notifies the listener that the launch is done, and, if it failed, an exception with information about why it failed.

    • Method Detail

      • notify

        void notify(IOException e)
        Notifies the listener that the launch is done, and, if it failed, an exception with information about why it failed.
        Parameters:
        e - an exception if the launch failed, or null if the launch succeeded.
